++ INQUISITORIAL SEAL — ORDO HERETICUS ++
------------------------------------------------
By order of the Holy Inquisition:

The commanding officer of the 412th is under suspicion of heresy.
Observe. Record. Do not act without sanction.
Trust no one. Not the Commissar. Not your own squad.

If the line falls, it falls cleansed.

Thought for the day: a small mind is a tidy mind.
